#) Iterating Over a Map:
    - You can use a for...of loop to iterate over the elements of a Map:
        // Create a Map
        const fruits = new Map([
            ["apples", 500],
            ["bananas", 300],
            ["oranges", 200]
        ]);

        // Iterate over the map elements
        let text = "";
        for (const x of fruits) {
            text += x + "<br>";
        }

        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = text;

